{"title":"海鸥（外二首）","authors":["冀汸"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冀汸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海和天的空阔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白昼与黑夜轮番占领"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮给雾，轮给风，轮给雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只由于有了你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——快乐的伴侣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们航行在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才不再是寂寞的生物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有名字的小岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔民的家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔船的避风港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手的航标……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，不仅仅是这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它还是大地的眼睛："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜望着大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有没有奔来凶险的风暴？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在最高的巉岩上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也是大地的眼睛："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里，凝视着大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守到它点亮满天星斗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨，凝视着大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等来它抛出燃烧的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近烈士陵园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花岗石的台阶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一级一级，把我托上来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地，一步一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近你们身旁……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，亲爱的同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们醒着，全醒着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直注视着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街铺了一条，又一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼矗起一幢，再一幢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖好文化馆，还要盖医院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了剧场，还要有电视差转台……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直聆听着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海涛在枕边唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支从洪荒时代唱起的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在遥远的将来，越唱越响的歌……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}